  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“A surreal 3D puzzle-platformer where you navigate dreamlike worlds using a wingsuit, swinging, rail grinding, and logic puzzles to complete missions.”</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dear Agent,</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for cooperating with <strong>CBIF</strong> (Central Bear Intelligence Facility).<br>Our mission: gather knowledge from every corner of the universe. And for that, we need <strong><i>you</i></strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/6449f4fe48051139d210f449f5eeec15.poster.avif?t=1747050965\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/6449f4fe48051139d210f449f5eeec15.webm?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/6449f4fe48051139d210f449f5eeec15.mp4?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Required Traits:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧼 Sleek and well-groomed furr (strict grooming protocol)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 A love for chaos, puzzles, and the unexplored</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 Willpower to tackle 40+ levels of platforming and problem-solving</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 Courage to collect 8 Enochian Fragments across the mysterious Island of Roo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 Grit to battle Kael, the Keeper of Dimensions, in a final 4-phase showdown</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/7bbdd6b6ba084fda8d9c17865f725107.poster.avif?t=1747050965\" width=602 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/7bbdd6b6ba084fda8d9c17865f725107.webm?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/7bbdd6b6ba084fda8d9c17865f725107.mp4?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mission Overview:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake on the <strong>Island of Roo</strong>, floating at the edge of the universe. CBIF's most critical mission awaits.<br>Each of Roo’s four sister islands contains surreal “Dreams” — bizarre environments that power ancient crystals.<br>Complete them all to unlock Roo’s core. Then, and only then, may you confront Kael and forge the <strong>mystical Enochian Cube</strong> — a construct of forgotten knowledge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/ad72ca0b78f143138a3011c1d84665bc.poster.avif?t=1747050965\" width=644 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/ad72ca0b78f143138a3011c1d84665bc.webm?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/ad72ca0b78f143138a3011c1d84665bc.mp4?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Objectives:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Conquer surreal Dreams across 4 interlinked islands<br>✅ Solve 40+ intense platforming and puzzle challenges<br>✅ Collect 8 Enochian Fragments (2 per island)<br>✅ Unlock powerful abilities<br>✅ Defeat Kael and forge the Cube</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/56a4a74b1e4217061e1153f086624760.poster.avif?t=1747050965\" width=644 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/56a4a74b1e4217061e1153f086624760.webm?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/56a4a74b1e4217061e1153f086624760.mp4?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mission Requirements:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No handholding.<br>No excuses.<br>Just you, your paws, and the chaos of Roo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Report for duty, Agent Furr.</strong><br>It’s time to bear the burden of knowledge.<br>The fate of the universe may rest on your furr.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you learn to bear?</strong> 🐻</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“A surreal 3D puzzle-platformer where you navigate dreamlike worlds using a wingsuit, swinging, rail grinding, and logic puzzles to complete missions.”</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dear Agent,</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for cooperating with <strong>CBIF</strong> (Central Bear Intelligence Facility).<br>Our mission: gather knowledge from every corner of the universe. And for that, we need <strong><i>you</i></strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/6449f4fe48051139d210f449f5eeec15.poster.avif?t=1747050965\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/6449f4fe48051139d210f449f5eeec15.webm?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/6449f4fe48051139d210f449f5eeec15.mp4?t=1747050965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Required Traits:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧼 Sleek and well-groomed furr (strict grooming protocol)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 A love for chaos, puzzles, and the unexplored</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 Willpower to tackle 40+ levels of platforming and problem-solving</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 Courage to collect 8 Enochian Fragments across the mysterious Island of Roo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 Grit to battle Kael, the Keeper of Dimensions, in a final 4-phase showdown</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789890/extras/7bbdd6b6ba084fd